> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=T, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	df<-ifelse(transpose, t(df), df)
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	head(d)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }
> wrapHclust(ecmb.filter, ft)

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=T, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	head(df)
+ 	df<-ifelse(transpose, t(df), df)
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	head(df)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }
> 
> wrapHclust(ecmb.filter, ft)

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=F, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=F, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	print(class(df))
+ 	ifelse(transpose, print('T'), print('F'))
+ 	df<-t(df)
+ 	print(head(df))
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	head(df)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }
> wrapHclust(ecmb.filter, ft)

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=F, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	print(class(df))
+ 	ifelse(transpose, print(head(t(df))), print(head(df)))
+ 	df<-t(df)
+ 	print(head(df))
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	head(df)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }
> 
> wrapHclust(ecmb.filter, ft)

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=F, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	print(class(df))
+ 	ifelse(transpose, print(head(t(df))), print(head(df)))
+ 	#df<-t(df)
+ 	#print(head(df))
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	#head(df)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }
> wrapHclust(ecmb.filter, ft, transpose=F)

> wrapHclust<-function(df, ft, idCol=1,
+ 	transpose=F, d.meth="euclidean", d.p = 2,
+ 	h.method = "average"
+  ){
+  	if(!is.null(idCol) | idCol !=0){
+ 		idCol<-ifelse(is.character(idCol), colNum(x, idCol), idCol)
+ 		row.names(df)<-df[,idCol]
+ 		df<-df[,setdiff(1:ncol(df), idCol)]
+ 	}
+ 	print(class(df))
+ 	ifelse(transpose, print(head(t(df))), print(head(df)))
+ 	print(
+ 		ifelse(transpose, head(t(df)), head(df) )
+ 	)
+ 		
+ 	#df<-t(df)
+ 	#print(head(df))
+ 	d<-dist(df, method=d.meth, p=d.p)
+ 	#head(df)
+ 	#h<-hclust(d, method=h.method)
+ }

> tabulate_H_Clusters<-function(h, ft, idCol=7, ks=c(2) ){
+ 	hc_table <- data.frame(
+ 		Sample = ft[, idCol]
+ 	)
+ 	for (k in ks){
+ 		if(k <= nrow(hc_table)){
+ 			c=data.frame(c=cutree(h, k))
+ 			c$Sample = row.names(c)
+ 			hc_table<-merge(
+ 				hc_table, c,
+ 				by = 'Sample'
+ 			)
+ 			name<-paste("k_eq_", k, sep='')
+ 			names(hc_table)[grep('c', names(hc_table))]<-name
+ 		}
+ 	}
+ 	hc_table
+ }
